        <Parent_String>weather and related phenomena [300162300], earth sciences concepts [300068654], physical sciences concepts [300065446], scientific concepts [300056006], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
